item.dc:creator: @xXSh0ckXx xXSh0ckXx
item.description:
@xXSh0ckXx wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:4, topic:537216”][quote author=SpectralResort link=topic=656033.msg4390685#msg4390685 date=1387397087]
iv’e herd so many bad things about PI, that i wouldn’t even recommend it.
[/quote]
The reason PI is “so bad” is because people download it and add code into it improperly, and cram content in the server improperly, and do nothing OOP, making the server crap (let alone the client) then they release it. Everyone sees all the cool content and download the source, then continue the bad practices they see in the server and make it EVEN WORSE. And eventually they release that, and so on. That’s why it’s bad. Maybe if people would take half a minute to learn and understand java before starting RSPS it wouldn’t be shit and we wouldn’t see garbage releases like Trisidia and Deathlypvpz.

/rant

OP make sure they aren’t disabled in Config.java[/quote]
Look son, what a legend!

Btw. You forgot Insidia X l0l

Still the best way is to code your own Pi from scratch. And no, If you change from PI to example Delta, it’s not a different Language. Java is java l0l.
